data.description: Detached, well-maintained two-family located in Morris Park. The top floor has 3 bedrooms, a spacious open living room/dining room,   and a large EIK.  Fully modernized approximately 6 years ago.  The first floor was updated approximately 15 years ago and includes 3 bedrooms, a large living room, and a spacious eat-in kitchen.  The oversized lot is approximately 5135 sq ft. Plenty of parking with a detached two-car garage and a long, private driveway   Partial basement for storage, heating, and a laundry room. The first floor is to be vacant on August 15, 2023.  The second floor is occupied by family and will be vacant by the middle of December 2023.
